headline: TKO Group Holdings to Participate in Morgan Stanley Technology, Media & Telecom Conference
summary: NEW YORK, February 11, 2025--TKO Group Holdings, Inc. (NYSE: TKO), a premium sports and sports entertainment company, announced that its President and Chief Operating Officer, Mark Shapiro, will participate in the Morgan Stanley Technology, Media & Telecom Conference on Monday, March 3, 2025 at 3:20 p.m. Eastern Time (12:20 p.m. Pacific Time) in San Francisco, CA.

headline: UFC AND THORNE ANNOUNCE ENHANCED GLOBAL PARTNERSHIP RENEWAL
summary: UFC, the world's premier mixed martial arts organization and part of TKO Group Holdings (NYSE: TKO), and Thorne, the leader in science-backed health and wellness solutions, today announced a renewal of their global partnership, featuring enhancements that will strengthen the collaboration.
